{"tid":1184252,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)哭泣的女人 陰兒房/兒凶4>1>2","createTime":"2019-06-03T13:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T18:00:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15e05c51ffbb2d994eb03efc82dc6eaba9c8b745","tid":1184252,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=220cfcf7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b433b16e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=d908aaf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://images5.fanpop.com/image/photos/24600000/Insidious-insidious-24669369-1280-536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages5.fanpop.com%2Fimage%2Fphotos%2F24600000%2FInsidious-insidious-24669369-1280-536.jpg&h=1976a693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.當社會工作者兼寡婦安娜&middot;賈西亞於1973年洛杉磯撫養她的兩個孩子時，她被要求配合調查，直到安娜開始探視一件犯罪事件的深處後，她發現該案件與可怕的超自然事件之間存在著驚人的相似之處，這些事件一直困擾著她的家人。在獲得當地信仰治療師的幫助下，她發現墨西哥民間傳說的女鬼憂羅娜已盯上了自己，且將不惜一切代價奪走她的孩子<br />\n<br />\n繼前集的事件過後，靈媒愛麗絲&middot;莉尼爾到新墨西哥州附近調查一棟房屋中的超自然事件，同時這也是她過去常住的房子..<br />\n<br />\n3.蕊娜(Renai)與喬許(Josh Lambert)與三個小孩搬到一間新房子。有一天兒子發生意外並從此昏迷不醒，之後家裡便發生許多神秘事件，不得不請靈媒過來解決。<br />\n<br />\n4.故事緊隨前集，在小男孩被成功救出但父親卻被惡靈附體後，Lambert一家的惡夢才真正展開，背後的真相也逐漸浮出水面。<br />\n<br />\n10 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=c7ddb1fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=71e4cb46\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bc27165e4e0744f8e612d84670a766129bf3af","tid":1184252,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4e/The_Curse_of_La_Llorona_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4e%2FThe_Curse_of_La_Llorona_Poster.jpg&h=fcb12a2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe5bd7b4128e32601c92cd914f7989996de6031e","tid":1184252,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac